    <j.0:dossier_title xml:lang="en">Proposal for a COUNCIL REGULATION amending Regulation (EU) No 7/2010 opening and providing for the management of autonomous tariff quotas of the Union for certain agricultural and industrial products </j.0:dossier_title>
